<h3><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>Initiating an attack<o:p></o:p></span>=
</h3>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>To initiate an attack=
 on an
enemy ship, first select one of your military ships and then right-click the
enemy ship. As you hover over the enemy ship the mouse cursor will change t=
